        "content": "<p>The proof of <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=zmodAddCyclicAddEquiv#doc\">docs#zmodAddCyclicAddEquiv</a> takes a generator using the axiom of choice so you could probably just make an alternate version which takes a generator, and reprove the other version using it.</p>",
